{"tid":634731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"快訊！1萬公里遠距離戀愛 真野恵里菜將嫁現役西甲足球明星柴崎岳","createTime":"2018-04-19T13:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T15:00:55.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"082a327cc38c0935cc902beab77cee8937057f82","tid":634731,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"曾演出《大姊當家》、《月薪嬌妻》的演員真野恵里菜與足球明星柴崎岳宣布即最快將在今年夏天結婚，舉行快樂夏日婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-04-19/656/20180419004443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-04-19%2F656%2F20180419004443.jpg&h=63934d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真野恵里菜（左）曾與新垣結衣合演《月薪嬌妻》。<br />\n<br />\n兩人自2016年起透過友人介紹而認識，但柴崎岳在西班牙效力西甲球會基達菲，因此兩人進行著1萬公里的遠距離戀愛。柴崎岳2017年9月在比賽中左腳受傷而脫離比賽期間，真野恵里菜一直在身邊細心照顧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-04-19/656/20180419004445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-04-19%2F656%2F20180419004445.jpg&h=a5fc441a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日運動報大幅報導真野恵里菜（左）與足球明星柴崎岳婚訊。<br />\n<br />\n真野恵里菜過去以偶像歌手身分出身，曾是後藤真希、安倍夏美的同門師妹，因彈得一手好琴，常在演唱時展現琴藝，2013年往戲劇圈發展後表現不凡，被視為值得期待的新生代演員。"},{"pid":"5e7441d156184aa464895521f3a0daed42015e8f","tid":634731,"uid":39253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://men-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/a4185c8ca811e3f92243857ad31121e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmen-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fa4185c8ca811e3f92243857ad31121e2.jpg&h=da46d9ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"830503b6f85ece986c8ae5a9719dc3b15044c051","tid":634731,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-04-19/656/20180419004443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg